    "name": {
      "zh": "SIG MPX 9x19 冲锋枪",
      "en": "SIG MPX 9x19 submachine gun"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "MPX",
      "en": "MPX"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "由于其各项构成要素均与AR系列步枪相似，SIG MPX自诩能让AR使用者以最快的速度掌握使用。短行程导气活塞使SIG MPX能够全面地使用各种9mm弹药而无需调整导气阀。全尺寸导轨可安装多种瞄准镜和瞄具设备。",
      "en": "The SIG Sauer MPX submachine gun boasts an unprecedented operation speed in the familiar form factor of the AR platform. Short-stroke gas piston allows SIG MPX to use the full range of 9 mm ammunition without any adjustments to the gas valve. The full-sized mount provides the means of installing a wide range of scopes and sighting devices."
    },
